---
import "../styles/why-choose-us.css";
---

<section class="trust-cta">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="trust-card">
            <h2>Ready to Grow Your Business?</h2>

            <p>
                Whether you're looking for more leads, higher rankings or better
                marketing performance, let's build a strategy tailored to your
                business.
            </p>

            <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">
                Book Your Free Strategy Call
            </a>
            <br>
            <br>
            <div class="trust-points">
                <span>★★★★★ <strong>5.0 Rating</strong></span>

                <span>•</span>

                <span>MSME Registered Agency</span>

                <span>•</span>

                <span>Real Client Results</span>

                <span>•</span>

                <span>Serving Clients Across India, Australia & Beyond</span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-logos">
                <div class="trust-logo">
                    <img
                        src="/logos/MonkeyReach-Media-MSME-Registered.avif"
                        alt="MonkeyReach MSME Registered"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>

                <div class="trust-logo">
                    <img
                        src="/logos/MonkeyReach-Founder-Google-Ads-course-Certification.avif"
                        alt="Google Ads Certification"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>

                <div class="trust-logo">
                    <img
                        src="/logos/monkeyreach-founder-sahil-raajput-iide-certification-meta-ads.avif"
                        alt="Meta Ads Certification"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>

                <div class="trust-logo">
                    <img
                        src="/logos/monkeyreach-site-icon.webp"
                        alt="MonkeyReach"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="seo-content">
    <div class="container">
        <p>
            MonkeyReach is a founder-led digital marketing agency built on
            hands-on experience since 2019. Founder Sahil Raajput progressed
            from SEO content writing to technical SEO, on-page SEO, off-page
            SEO, local SEO, Google Search Console, Google Analytics, content
            strategy, website performance optimisation, conversion optimisation,
            YouTube SEO and performance marketing.
        </p>

        <p>
            MonkeyReach is an MSME-registered business (UDYAM-HR-11-0066924)
            operating under NIC 73100 – Advertising & Market Research. Every
            strategy is backed by practical experience, real client projects,
            measurable case studies, publicly available results and transparent
            reporting rather than marketing claims.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
